			Candescite can also be manually generated by using a Worldly Scroll
			'''
	}

	ShouldGenerateSkyStructure: {
		Label: Generate Storm Shrine
		Tooltip: 
			'''
			Determines whether the Storm Shrine should be generated upon world creation. 
			Disabling this structure will prevent a boss from being summoned.
			The Storm Shrine can also be manually generated by using a Worldly Scroll
